{"tid":2252584,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】申才恩原圖美腿完勝網紅P圖筷子腳　網民心心眼：自然美","createTime":"2020-10-21T14:30:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T15:16:40.000Z","uid":16659,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d0aefe19a1fbb64e6393f1a8dee87ca360b60d3b","tid":2252584,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T14:30:59.000Z","msg":"近年P圖、美顏濾鏡盛行，早已進入了一個有圖甚至有片都無真相的年代，尤其是一眾所謂的網紅，無論樣貌身材幾乎全部一式一樣，很少敢以原圖示人。現年29歲的韓國模特兒申才恩是網紅兼新一代IG女神，她早前就於IG post了她的原圖靚相大曬一對白滑美腿。有別於那些網紅會將她們的腳P成又長又直且超級幼的筷子腳，大小腿一樣幼，申才恩的雙腿粗幼比例極之正常，即使大腿看來比較粗，但線條顯得好靚好自然，不少網民均睇到心心眼，並大讚她展現出自然美。"},{"pid":"82481893d36290c2a09b10d087eaaa8c3e10d126","tid":2252584,"uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T14:31:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201021/395605079962423296537268.jpeg/Y-9RYj48nGJie0iVv93rK59PFu_p3uSYsGHr2LBh69g?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201021%2F395605079962423296537268.jpeg%2FY-9RYj48nGJie0iVv93rK59PFu_p3uSYsGHr2LBh69g%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=1f33e49c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201021/395605972904579072980612.jpeg/FeZpEHS5qLerHzAT3gB8BYwLpHZx8sD0p8-NOKfPjTg?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201021%2F395605972904579072980612.jpeg%2FFeZpEHS5qLerHzAT3gB8BYwLpHZx8sD0p8-NOKfPjTg%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=30b5991e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201021/395605975178022912054379.jpeg/mQXtEyfbMUN0L-9GupvOQbGpuRKW67p4dAXRUHQF0VA?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201021%2F395605975178022912054379.jpeg%2FmQXtEyfbMUN0L-9GupvOQbGpuRKW67p4dAXRUHQF0VA%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=7735baad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"82164cbf8026ed4b1566e35f3d8406485bbfb49e","tid":2252584,"uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":1,